Information on Introduction to the Theory of Computation
Introduction to the Theory of Computation
Author:
Michael Sipser 
Published by the
PWS Publishing Company.
Textbook for an upper division undergraduate and introductory graduate
level course covering automata theory, computability theory, and
complexity theory.  
The  first edition is now available.  
I am maintaining a
 list of errata
for the first edition.
The 
preliminary edition
had been discontinued.  
I am no longer maintaining its
errata site.